<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>中国新闻|今日突发新闻 |路透社</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/</link><description>Reuters.com 是您获取最新中国新闻故事和时事的在线来源，确保我们的读者及时了解任何突发新闻动态 - 由 RSSHub 提供支持</description><lastBuildDate>Thu, 26 Sep 2024 09:15:38 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>美国制裁许可证即将到期威胁俄罗斯的人民币流动性</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/currencies/impending-expiry-us-sanctions-licence-threatens-russias-yuan-liquidity-2024-09-26/</link><description>从事进口和支付业务的消息人士告诉路透社，美国允许涉及俄罗斯金融基础设施支柱的交易的许可证即将到期，可能会使俄罗斯企业进行人民币交易变得更加困难且成本更高。</description><pubDate>Thu, 26 Sep 2024 08:57:06 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/currencies/impending-expiry-us-sanctions-licence-threatens-russias-yuan-liquidity-2024-09-26/</guid></item><item><title>中国称其导弹发射是例行合法安排</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-says-its-missile-launch-is-routine-legitimate-arrangement-2024-09-26/</link><description>中国国防部周四表示，中国发射洲际弹道导弹是为了进行武器试验和训练，是例行合法安排。</description><pubDate>Thu, 26 Sep 2024 08:43:21 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-says-its-missile-launch-is-routine-legitimate-arrangement-2024-09-26/</guid></item><item><title>随着中国进口激增，印度钢铁制造商寻求更高关税</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/indian-steelmakers-seek-higher-tariffs-chinese-imports-surge-2024-09-26/</link><description>路透社看到的一封来自行业协会的信函显示，印度钢铁制造商呼吁政府将钢铁进口关税提高一倍，以遏制来自中国的廉价钢铁出货量激增。</description><pubDate>Thu, 26 Sep 2024 08:10:58 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/indian-steelmakers-seek-higher-tariffs-chinese-imports-surge-2024-09-26/</guid></item><item><title>随着中国承诺采取更多刺激措施，伦敦股市上涨；石油库存下跌</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/europe/london-shares-gain-china-pledges-more-stimulus-oil-stocks-fall-2024-09-26/</link><description>英国股市周四上涨，受矿业股提振，中国最新承诺采取更多政策措施，引发了人们对世界第二大经济体好转的乐观情绪，而石油相关股票的下跌限制了涨幅。</description><pubDate>Thu, 26 Sep 2024 07:42:07 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/europe/london-shares-gain-china-pledges-more-stimulus-oil-stocks-fall-2024-09-26/</guid></item><item><title>中国希望通过灵活的定价解决方案与欧盟就电动汽车关税争端达成共识</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/china-targets-consensus-with-eu-ev-tariff-dispute-through-flexible-pricing-2024-09-26/</link><description>中国商务部周四表示，中国和欧盟委员会的技术团队正在就电动汽车关税争端积极协商灵活的价格承诺解决方案。</description><pubDate>Thu, 26 Sep 2024 07:32:34 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/china-targets-consensus-with-eu-ev-tariff-dispute-through-flexible-pricing-2024-09-26/</guid></item><item><title>中国股市反弹推动斯托克 600 指数接近历史新高</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/europe/china-rally-pushes-stoxx-600-close-record-highs-2024-09-26/</link><description>受中国新刺激措施的乐观情绪提振，欧洲股市周四上涨，投资者等待欧洲央行行长的言论。</description><pubDate>Thu, 26 Sep 2024 07:22:41 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/europe/china-rally-pushes-stoxx-600-close-record-highs-2024-09-26/</guid></item><item><title>大熊猫对抵达香港 使香港总数创历史新高</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/panda-pair-arrive-hong-kong-boost-citys-total-highest-ever-2024-09-26/</link><description>周四，北京送给香港的礼物大熊猫“安安”和“可可”抵达中国领土，官员们在香港国际机场大张旗鼓地欢迎它们，停机坪上铺着红地毯，并摆满了熊猫玩具。</description><pubDate>Thu, 26 Sep 2024 07:22:07 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/panda-pair-arrive-hong-kong-boost-citys-total-highest-ever-2024-09-26/</guid></item><item><title>中国誓言“必要支出”以实现经济增长目标</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-vows-necessary-spending-hit-economic-growth-target-2024-09-26/</link><description>中国领导人周四承诺部署“必要的财政支出”，以实现今年约5%的经济增长目标，承认新问题，并提高了市场对本周宣布的措施之外的新刺激措施的预期。</description><pubDate>Thu, 26 Sep 2024 07:03:56 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-vows-necessary-spending-hit-economic-growth-target-2024-09-26/</guid></item><item><title>外国投资者远距离为中国的经济刺激计划喝彩</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/foreign-investors-cheer-chinas-stimulus-distance-2024-09-26/</link><description>随着市场对中国自疫情大流行以来最大规模刺激措施的兴奋情绪平息下来，外国投资者现在开始询问，1140亿美元的工具包是否能提供扭转低迷股市所需的动力。</description><pubDate>Thu, 26 Sep 2024 06:29:04 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/foreign-investors-cheer-chinas-stimulus-distance-2024-09-26/</guid></item><item><title>巴西航空公司寻求从中国商飞购买飞机</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/aerospace-defense/brazilian-airline-seeks-buy-planes-chinas-comac-2024-09-26/</link><description>巴西的Total Linhas Aereas是一家小型货运和包机航空公司，其目标是成为亚洲以外第一家从中国国有飞机制造商购买飞机的公司，该公司正试图打入由西方制造商主导的全球客机市场。</description><pubDate>Thu, 26 Sep 2024 05:07:15 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/aerospace-defense/brazilian-airline-seeks-buy-planes-chinas-comac-2024-09-26/</guid></item><item><title>Stellantis首席执行官遵循中国路线以避免电动汽车关税“陷阱”</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/stellantis-ceo-follows-chinese-route-avoid-ev-tariff-trap-2024-09-26/</link><description>尽管首席执行官卡洛斯·塔瓦雷斯痛斥欧洲和美国的关税是反竞争的，但斯特兰蒂斯希望采用中国电动汽车制造商的低成本思维，但这家全球第四大汽车制造商如果想取得成功，就必须克服大西洋两岸的贸易壁垒。</description><pubDate>Thu, 26 Sep 2024 05:04:46 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/stellantis-ceo-follows-chinese-route-avoid-ev-tariff-trap-2024-09-26/</guid></item><item><title>早间买盘：中国给市场另一个欢呼的理由</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/europe/global-markets-view-europe-2024-09-26/</link><description>Rae Wee 对欧洲和全球市场未来一天的展望</description><pubDate>Thu, 26 Sep 2024 04:33:43 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/europe/global-markets-view-europe-2024-09-26/</guid></item><item><title>宜家购物中心部门为耗资 10 亿美元的上海开发项目敞开大门</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/ikea-shopping-mall-arm-opens-doors-1-bln-shanghai-development-2024-09-26/</link><description>宜家旗下购物中心业务英格卡中心周五在上海开设了一个综合体项目，耗资超过 80 亿元人民币（11.4 亿美元），是该集团在中国最大的单笔投资。</description><pubDate>Thu, 26 Sep 2024 04:03:32 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/ikea-shopping-mall-arm-opens-doors-1-bln-shanghai-development-2024-09-26/</guid></item><item><title>中国针对加拿大关税展开反歧视调查</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/china-launches-anti-discriminatory-probe-against-canadas-tariffs-2024-09-26/</link><description>中国商务部周四表示，中国对加拿大采取的限制性措施（包括对中国电动汽车、钢铁和铝产品加征关税）发起反歧视调查。</description><pubDate>Thu, 26 Sep 2024 03:46:51 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/china-launches-anti-discriminatory-probe-against-canadas-tariffs-2024-09-26/</guid></item><item><title>中国将向有需要的人提供一次性救济</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-give-one-off-handouts-needy-2024-09-26/</link><description>一份政府声明称，中国将在下周国庆节前向弱势群体发放一次性补贴。</description><pubDate>Thu, 26 Sep 2024 03:17:57 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-give-one-off-handouts-needy-2024-09-26/</guid></item></channel></rss>